<color=#00fffb>Welcome to Neon Abyss! We strongly suggest everyone to try the experimental branch for the latest content and rapid updates!</color>
<color=#00fffb>If you encounter serious bugs, please don't forget use Save&Load.</color>
<color=#ec6fff>If you have any suggestions, feedback or bug report, please join our Discord.gg/veewo.</color>

<color=#ffe866>The new DLC Alter Ego is now live!</color>

<color=#00fffb>1.3.4.4 Exp-Branch</color> 
* Pet Peter, Blue Doctor, and Grey now have baby forms.
* Pet Peter, Blue Doctor, and Grey can be combined to a new pet.
* New gun "Matrix" is added, try it out!
* Several new monsters have been added.

<color=#00fffb>1.3.4.1</color> 
* Added The Titan: Prometheus. As the ruler of the new era, the Titan Group finally shows up!
* Added 2 new special Managers: Cursed Athena and Ares. You can check their specific information at the bar.
* Added a new normal Boss: God of Makeup.
* Added 2 new special levels: You need to get a special ticket to enter this level.
* Happy Chinese New Year! Here is the special seed: 20210212, let's set off firecrackers together!

<color=#00fffb>1.3.2.56 Exp-Branch</color>

* All character skins are open for testing for one week.
* The Titan Boss Prometheus is open for testing for one week.
* Added 2 new special Managers: Cursed Athena and Ares. You can check their specific information at the bar.

<color=#00fffb>1.2.5.7 Default-Branch</color>

<color=#ec6fff>Merry Christmas! We've got a special holiday seed for you: 20131127, you can build a snowman in the game! </color>

Major Changes: 

* The Lab(Basement level 2)is now open, you can now customize the monster encounters! 
* Added 3 Sets of items, obtain enough items in a Set to activate Set powers! 
* Added new jump related items, you could win fights without ever firing a shot! 
* Tweaked explosion related items, synergies between the explosion items are now enhanced. 
* Added 6 new soundtrack in the game, let's rock! 

New nodes in the unlocking true: 

* WARRIOR STATUE - GUARDIAN: You will get a random blessing if you die 3 runs in a roll. 
* Reroll Cube: There is a chance that a carryable cube will appear in the shop, which has many magical effects! Lift and throw it! 
* Golden Secret: There is a chance that you may find golden creatures in battle rooms. 
* New Pain room:it will drop an item if you get hurt on the 6th time in this room. 
Added Random Character choice with a random item.   

Other changes: 

  * Added a series of puzzle-solving rooms (you will be rewarded if you solve them) 
* Remake Ming's skill: he can now preview the result of the next egg hatch 
* Pets will now get stronger the more pets you have 
* Added a new big worm monster 
* Added a Special Chest Shop 
* Added more battle rooms 
* Added item effect activation indicators 
* Added a new type of Challenge room, it will reward you even if you get hit. 
* Abyssal difficulty can be accessed any time once unlocked 
* Update to monster bullet appearance 
* Reduced glare issue when bullets or lasers fills the screen 
* Added item effect indicator 
* Tweaks to Shooting game room, it now drops items other than weapons 
* Tweaks to Brick game room, drops more varied items 
* Added a new piano song 
* Fire Cracker item now only works in combat 
* Thunder and Summer buffed，radius increases with jump times 

